T1  - Mutual Fund Fragility, Dealer Liquidity Provision, and the Pricing of Municipal Bonds
AU  - Li, Yi
AU  - O’Hara, Maureen
AU  - Zhou, Xing (Alex)
Y1  - 2023/09/21
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2024/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4912
